citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:57 am on
02/25/2015.
APHIS VMO attempted to contact licensee via telephone and left a message. APHIS VMO rang the door bell at the
facility and waited 30 minutes. Licensee later contacted APHIS VMO via telephone.
